query:
SELECT
            p.id as project_id,
            d.id as "id?",
            d.status as "status?: crate::db::models::DeploymentStatus"
        FROM unnest($1::uuid[]) AS p(id)
        LEFT JOIN deployments d ON d.project_id = p.id
            AND d.is_active = TRUE
            AND d.deployment_group = 'default'
